title: My Youtube Channel

embed.description: Hello! I make a variety of League of Legends videos and am always open for suggestions for videos.

body:
Hey everyone. I am a new youtuber who makes a variety of top 5 videos and a few small clips here and there. I am looking to start making other content such as montages. I'd really appreciate it if you could come check out my channel and give some advice. Also, if you subscribed/liked my content, that'd be much appreciated. Thanks,

Anibaedan
